ca.ualberta.cmput301.t03.inventory

Class UserInventoryFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301.t03.inventory.UserInventoryFragment

  • public class UserInventoryFragment
extends java.lang.Object
    Fragment that displays the User's Inventory in a ListView. By clicking the listed Items here the user can inspect, edit and delete. The User can add an item by pressing the FloatingActionButton.
